          "text": "The point is not to guarantee an instant result. The point is to stop letting silence be the guarantee of nothing changing at all. When you speak, you create the possibility for change. You shift the room. You position yourself differently. You refuse to be invisible. Even if one conversation does not solve everything, it breaks the pattern of silence that has been protecting your stagnation. Start speaking and watch what happens over time."
